/*

 old UNIX, the pekwm-dev theme by ruabag (ruabag@gmail.com)
 Last modified 20050314 by shared.

 Theme is labeled for pekwm-dev-20050227.

 In short that means it works attleast with the mentioned theme
 snapshot. Usually it should work fine with newer pekwm-dev releases,
 but if you notice it not working after an update, check in for a
 new version of the theme.

 Buttons and its use:
 | Menu |------Title bar-------| Maximize | Shade | Close | Iconify | Maximum Fill |


 Changelog:
   20050314, modified to comply to pekwm-dev theme guidelines by shared <themes@adresh.com>.
     - Added missing required theme structure.
     - Added menu separators.
     - Added submenu arrows.
     - Modified theme directory name to show what pekwm-dev version theme is for.
     - Fixed indention.
     - Modified titlebar text colours so that one can tell the active client of a frame.

*/


